9. Interview Question
What is RAG?
Answer:

RAG stands for Retrieval-Augmented Generation. Instead of sending the entire PDF to the LLM, we retrieve only the most relevant chunks using vector similarity search and provide them as context to the model. This improves accuracy, reduces hallucination, and lowers token cost.

